<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Becados UTEPSA · Campus Virtual</title>
<style>
:root{
  --azul-900:#0A2E4D;
  --azul-800:#0F3D63;
  --azul-700:#15497A;
  --azul-100:#E4ECF4;
  --oro-600:#B9881F;
  --oro-100:#FAF1DC;
  --verde-700:#1F7A4D;
  --verde-100:#E3F3E9;
  --rojo-700:#B0392A;
  --rojo-100:#F8E6E2;
  --crema:#F7F4EC;
  --crema-2:#F1ECE0;
  --tinta:#1E2430;
  --tinta-suave:#5B6472;
  --linea:#DCD5C2;
  --blanco:#FFFFFF;
  --radius:10px;
  --serif:'Source Serif 4','Iowan Old Style','Georgia',serif;
  --sans:'Inter',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

*{box-sizing:border-box;}
html,body{margin:0;padding:0;}
body{
  font-family:var(--sans);
  background:var(--crema);
  color:var(--tinta);
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
  *{animation-duration:0.01ms !important; transition-duration:0.01ms !important;}
}

a{color:inherit;}
button{font-family:inherit;}

/* ======== Utility ======== */
.visually-hidden{position:absolute;left:-9999px;}
.hidden{display:none !important;}

/* ======== Topbar institucional ======== */
.topbar{
  background:var(--azul-900);
  color:#fff;
  font-size:12.5px;
  letter-spacing:.02em;
  padding:6px 0;
}
.topbar .wrap{
  max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;
  display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
  opacity:.85;
}

/* ======== Login screen ======== */
.login-screen{
  min-height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  padding:40px 20px;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 15% 20%, rgba(15,61,99,0.05), transparent 40%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 85% 80%, rgba(185,136,31,0.06), transparent 40%),
    var(--crema);
}
.login-wrap{
  width:100%;
  max-width:920px;
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1.1fr 1fr;
  background:var(--blanco);
  border-radius:16px;
  overflow:hidden;
  box-shadow:0 30px 60px -20px rgba(10,46,77,0.25), 0 0 0 1px rgba(10,46,77,0.04);
}
@media (max-width:760px){
  .login-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
}

.login-side{
  background:linear-gradient(160deg, var(--azul-900) 0%, var(--azul-700) 100%);
  color:#fff;
  padding:48px 40px;
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  justify-content:space-between;
  min-height:420px;
}
.login-side::before{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;
  inset:0;
  background-image:
    repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 0px, rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 14px);
  pointer-events:none;
}
.brand-mark{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:12px;
  position:relative;
  z-index:1;
}
.brand-crest{
  width:46px;height:46px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--oro-600);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:var(--serif);
  font-weight:700;
  font-size:19px;
  color:var(--azul-900);
  flex-shrink:0;
  box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
}
.brand-text{font-family:var(--serif);}
.brand-text .top{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:.75;display:block;}
.brand-text .main{font-size:18px;font-weight:600;display:block;line-height:1.2;}

.login-side-quote{
  position:relative;z-index:1;
  margin-top:48px;
}
.login-side-quote .eyebrow{
  font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--oro-100);opacity:.8;margin-bottom:14px;
}
.login-side-quote h1{
  font-family:var(--serif);
  font-size:30px;
  line-height:1.25;
  font-weight:600;
  margin:0 0 16px 0;
}
.login-side-quote p{
  font-size:14.5px;
  line-height:1.65;
  opacity:.82;
  max-width:360px;
}
.login-stats{
  display:flex;gap:28px;margin-top:32px;position:relative;z-index:1;
}
.login-stats div{}
.login-stats strong{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:24px;display:block;font-weight:600;}
.login-stats span{font-size:11.5px;opacity:.7;letter-spacing:.02em;}

.login-form-side{
  padding:48px 44px;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
}
.login-form-side h2{
  font-family:var(--serif);
  font-size:23px;
  margin:0 0 6px 0;
  font-weight:600;
}
.login-form-side .sub{
  color:var(--tinta-suave);
  font-size:13.5px;
  margin:0 0 28px 0;
}

.role-switch{
  display:flex;
  background:var(--crema-2);
  border-radius:999px;
  padding:4px;
  margin-bottom:26px;
  border:1px solid var(--linea);
}
.role-switch button{
  flex:1;
  border:none;
  background:transparent;
  padding:9px 12px;
  border-radius:999px;
  font-size:13px;
  font-weight:600;
  color:var(--tinta-suave);
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .18s ease;
}
.role-switch button.active{
  background:var(--azul-900);
  color:#fff;
  box-shadow:0 4px 10px -4px rgba(10,46,77,0.5);
}

.field{margin-bottom:16px;}
.field label{
  display:block;
  font-size:12.5px;
  font-weight:600;
  color:var(--tinta);
  margin-bottom:6px;
  letter-spacing:.01em;
}
.field input, .field select{
  width:100%;
  padding:11px 13px;
  border:1.5px solid var(--linea);
  border-radius:8px;
  font-size:14px;
  font-family:inherit;
  background:var(--blanco);
  color:var(--tinta);
  transition:border-color .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease;
}
.field input:focus, .field select:focus{
  outline:none;
  border-color:var(--azul-700);
  box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--azul-100);
}
.field .hint{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--tinta-suave);margin-top:5px;}

.btn-primary{
  width:100%;
  padding:13px;
  background:var(--azul-900);
  color:#fff;
  border:none;
  border-radius:8px;
  font-size:14.5px;
  font-weight:600;
  cursor:pointer;
  margin-top:6px;
  transition:background .15s ease, transform .1s ease;
}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--azul-700);}
.btn-primary:active{transform:scale(0.99);}

.demo-note{
  margin-top:20px;
  padding:13px 14px;
  background:var(--oro-100);
  border:1px solid #E8D8AA;
  border-radius:8px;
  font-size:12px;
  line-height:1.55;
  color:#6B5212;
}
.demo-note strong{color:#4A3A0D;}

.login-foot{
  margin-top:auto;
  padding-top:20px;
  font-size:11.5px;
  color:var(--tinta-suave);
}

/* ======== App shell ======== */
.app{display:none;min-height:100vh;flex-direction:column;}
.app.active{display:flex;}

.app-header{
  background:var(--blanco);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--linea);
  position:sticky;top:0;z-index:30;
}
.app-header-inner{
  max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:14px 24px;
}
.app-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;}
.app-brand .brand-crest{width:38px;height:38px;font-size:16px;}
.app-brand-text{font-family:var(--serif);}
.app-brand-text .top{font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tinta-suave);display:block;}
.app-brand-text .main{font-size:15.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--azul-900);display:block;line-height:1.2;}

.app-nav{display:flex;gap:4px;}
.app-nav button{
  border:none;background:transparent;
  padding:9px 16px;border-radius:7px;
  font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;
  color:var(--tinta-suave);
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .15s ease;
}
.app-nav button:hover{background:var(--crema-2);color:var(--tinta);}
.app-nav button.active{background:var(--azul-100);color:var(--azul-900);}

.app-user{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
.app-user-info{text-align:right;}
.app-user-info .name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;display:block;line-height:1.3;}
.app-user-info .role{font-size:11px;color:var(--tinta-suave);display:block;}
.avatar{
  width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--azul-800);color:#fff;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-size:13px;font-weight:700;font-family:var(--serif);
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.btn-logout{
  border:1.5px solid var(--linea);
  background:transparent;
  padding:8px 14px;
  border-radius:7px;
  font-size:12.5px;
  font-weight:600;
  color:var(--tinta-suave);
  cursor:pointer;
  margin-left:4px;
}
.btn-logout:hover{border-color:var(--rojo-700);color:var(--rojo-700);}

@media (max-width:880px){
  .app-nav{display:none;}
  .app-nav.mobile-visible{
    display:flex;position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;
    background:#fff;border-top:1px solid var(--linea);
    padding:8px 10px;justify-content:space-around;z-index:40;
  }
  .app-nav.mobile-visible button{flex:1;flex-direction:column;font-size:10.5px;padding:8px 4px;}
}

.app-main{
  flex:1;
  max-width:1180px;
  margin:0 auto;
  width:100%;
  padding:32px 24px 80px;
}

.view{display:none;}
.view.active{display:block;animation:fadeUp .35s ease;}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

.view-head{margin-bottom:26px;}
.view-head .eyebrow{
  font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--oro-600);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;
}
.view-head h1{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-size:27px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 6px 0;color:var(--azul-900);
}
.view-head p{color:var(--tinta-suave);font-size:14px;margin:0;max-width:640px;line-height:1.55;}

/* ======== Cards / stats ======== */
.stat-grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
  gap:16px;
  margin-bottom:28px;
}
@media (max-width:880px){.stat-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}}
.stat-card{
  background:var(--blanco);
  border:1px solid var(--linea);
  border-radius:12px;
  padding:18px 20px;
}
.stat-card .label{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--tinta-suave);font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:8px;}
.stat-card .value{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:30px;font-weight:600;color:var(--azul-900);line-height:1;}
.stat-card .value.gold{color:var(--oro-600);}
.stat-card .value.green{color:var(--verde-700);}
.stat-card .value.red{color:var(--rojo-700);}
.stat-card .sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--tinta-suave);margin-top:6px;}

.progress-bar-track{
  width:100%;height:9px;border-radius:99px;
  background:var(--crema-2);overflow:hidden;margin-top:10px;
}
.progress-bar-fill{
  height:100%;border-radius:99px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--oro-600), #D4A B2F);
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--oro-600), #D9AE3D);
  transition:width .5s ease;
}

.panel{
  background:var(--blanco);
  border:1px solid var(--linea);
  border-radius:14px;
  padding:24px;
  margin-bottom:22px;
}
.panel-head{
  display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;
  margin-bottom:18px;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.panel-head h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:18.5px;font-weight:600;margin:0;color:var(--azul-900);}
.panel-head .desc{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--tinta-suave);margin-top:4px;}

/* ======== Tables / lists ======== */
.table-wrap{overflow-x:auto;}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13.5px;}
thead th{
  text-align:left;
  font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;
  color:var(--tinta-suave);
  font-weight:700;
  padding:0 12px 10px;
  border-bottom:1.5px solid var(--linea);
}
tbody td{
  padding:13px 12px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--crema-2);
  vertical-align:middle;
}
tbody tr:hover{background:var(--crema);}
tbody tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}

.pill{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;
  padding:4px 10px;border-radius:99px;
  font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.01em;
}
.pill::before{content:"";width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;}
.pill.pendiente{background:var(--oro-100);color:#8A6510;}
.pill.pendiente::before{background:var(--oro-600);}
.pill.aprobada{background:var(--verde-100);color:var(--verde-700);}
.pill.aprobada::before{background:var(--verde-700);}
.pill.rechazada{background:var(--rojo-100);color:var(--rojo-700);}
.pill.rechazada::before{background:var(--rojo-700);}

.empty-state{
  text-align:center;padding:50px 20px;color:var(--tinta-suave);
}
.empty-state .icon{font-size:34px;margin-bottom:10px;opacity:.5;}
.empty-state p{font-size:13.5px;margin:0;}

/* ======== Forms ======== */
.form-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;}
@media (max-width:640px){.form-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
.form-grid .span2{grid-column:1/-1;}

.code-input-wrap{position:relative;}
.code-input-wrap input{
  text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;font-weight:700;font-family:monospace,var(--sans);
}
.code-badge{
  position:absolute;right:12px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);
  font-size:10.5px;color:var(--tinta-suave);
  background:var(--crema-2);padding:3px 8px;border-radius:6px;
  pointer-events:none;
}

.btn-secondary{
  padding:11px 18px;border-radius:8px;border:1.5px solid var(--linea);
  background:transparent;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--tinta);cursor:pointer;
}
.btn-secondary:hover{border-color:var(--azul-700);color:var(--azul-700);}

.btn-row{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:18px;flex-wrap:wrap;}

/* ======== Seal / stamp visual ======== */
.seal{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;
  border:1.5px dashed var(--oro-600);
  border-radius:8px;
  padding:6px 10px;
  font-size:11px;
  font-weight:700;
  color:var(--oro-600);
  letter-spacing:.04em;
  background:var(--oro-100);
  font-family:monospace,var(--sans);
}

/* ======== Jefatura: action buttons ======== */
.action-btns{display:flex;gap:6px;}
.btn-icon{
  width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:7px;border:1.5px solid var(--linea);
  background:transparent;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-size:14px;transition:all .15s ease;
}
.btn-icon.approve:hover{background:var(--verde-100);border-color:var(--verde-700);}
.btn-icon.reject:hover{background:var(--rojo-100);border-color:var(--rojo-700);}
.btn-icon.view:hover{background:var(--azul-100);border-color:var(--azul-700);}

/* ======== Modal ======== */
.modal-overlay{
  position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(10,30,50,0.45);
  display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:100;
  padding:20px;backdrop-filter:blur(2px);
}
.modal-overlay.active{display:flex;}
.modal{
  background:#fff;border-radius:14px;max-width:480px;width:100%;
  padding:26px;box-shadow:0 30px 60px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  max-height:88vh;overflow-y:auto;
}
.modal h3{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:18px;margin:0 0 4px 0;color:var(--azul-900);}
.modal .modal-sub{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--tinta-suave);margin:0 0 18px 0;}
.modal-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--crema-2);font-size:13px;}
.modal-row span:first-child{color:var(--tinta-suave);}
.modal-row span:last-child{font-weight:600;text-align:right;}

.toast-wrap{position:fixed;bottom:24px;right:24px;z-index:200;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}
.toast{
  background:var(--azul-900);color:#fff;padding:13px 18px;border-radius:9px;
  font-size:13px;font-weight:600;box-shadow:0 10px 25px -8px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
  animation:toastIn .25s ease;max-width:320px;
}
.toast.success{background:var(--verde-700);}
.toast.error{background:var(--rojo-700);}
@keyframes toastIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

.filter-tabs{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:18px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.filter-tabs button{
  border:1.5px solid var(--linea);background:transparent;
  padding:7px 14px;border-radius:99px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;
  color:var(--tinta-suave);cursor:pointer;
}
.filter-tabs button.active{background:var(--azul-900);color:#fff;border-color:var(--azul-900);}

.note-box{
  background:var(--azul-100);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;font-size:12.5px;
  color:var(--azul-900);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:18px;
}
.note-box strong{display:block;margin-bottom:3px;}

.footer-note{
  text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--tinta-suave);padding:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--linea);
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ============ LOGIN SCREEN ============ -->
<div class="login-screen" id="loginScreen">
  <div class="login-wrap">
    <div class="login-side">
      <div class="brand-mark">
        <div class="brand-crest">U</div>
        <div class="brand-text">
          <span class="top">Campus Virtual</span>
          <span class="main">UTEPSA</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="login-side-quote">
        <div class="eyebrow">Extensión · Becas y trabajo social</div>
        <h1>El registro de horas de tu beca, sin papel y sin esperar el aviso.</h1>
        <p>Cada actividad queda validada con el código que te entrega el responsable del lugar, y Jefatura de Becas confirma las horas directamente en el sistema.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="login-stats">
        <div><strong>0</strong><span>Planillas físicas</span></div>
        <div><strong>100%</strong><span>Trazabilidad</span></div>
        <div><strong>1</strong><span>Solo lugar de consulta</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="login-form-side">
      <h2>Iniciar sesión</h2>
      <p class="sub">Usa tu cuenta institucional de Campus Virtual.</p>

      <div class="role-switch">
        <button type="button" class="active" data-role="becado" onclick="setLoginRole('becado')">Soy becado/a</button>
        <button type="button" data-role="jefatura" onclick="setLoginRole('jefatura')">Jefatura de Becas</button>
      </div>

      <form id="loginForm" onsubmit="handleLogin(event)">
        <div class="field">
          <label for="loginUser" id="loginUserLabel">Código de estudiante</label>
          <input type="text" id="loginUser" placeholder="Ej. 2023104521" required>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="loginPass">Contraseña</label>
          <input type="password" id="loginPass" placeholder="••••••••" required>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary" id="loginSubmitBtn">Ingresar como becado/a</button>
      </form>

      <div class="demo-note">
        <strong>Modo demostración — Feria UTEPSA.</strong> Este login es simulado para la presentación del proyecto. Ingresa cualquier código y contraseña para entrar; el rol se elige arriba. En la versión final, el inicio de sesión se conecta directamente con las credenciales reales del Campus Virtual.
      </div>

      <div class="login-foot">Proyecto Feria UTEPSA 2026 · Estadística Empresarial</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============ APP: BECADO ============ -->
<div class="app" id="appBecado">
  <header class="app-header">
    <div class="app-header-inner">
      <div class="app-brand">
        <div class="brand-crest">U</div>
        <div class="app-brand-text"><span class="top">Campus Virtual</span><span class="main">Becados UTEPSA</span></div>
      </div>
      <nav class="app-nav" id="navBecado">
        <button data-view="inicio" class="active" onclick="goToView('becado','inicio')">Inicio</button>
        <button data-view="registrar" onclick="goToView('becado','registrar')">Registrar actividad</button>
        <button data-view="historial" onclick="goToView('becado','historial')">Historial</button>
      </nav>
      <div class="app-user">
        <div class="app-user-info">
          <span class="name" id="becadoNombre">María López</span>
          <span class="role" id="becadoBecaInfo">Beca Bachiller Destacado</span>
        </div>
        <div class="avatar" id="becadoAvatar">ML</div>
